data.title: Directors UK
data.text: Queen Sugar is produced for OWN by Warner Horizon Scripted Television and Executive Produced by Ava DuVernay and Oprah Winfry. 2019 This long running NBC series follows the Special Victims Unit, a specially trained squad of detectives in the New York City Police Department that investigate sexually related crimes. Featuring Mariska Hargaty and Ice T. 2022
